1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,300
Rainfall Mochi!

3
00:01:56,950 --> 00:02:00,420
Damn it! He went right back
to being strong again!

4
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:04,330
Gum-Gum...

5
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:06,990
Kong...

6
00:02:06,990 --> 00:02:08,340
Gun!

7
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,510
Donuts!

8
00:02:14,510 --> 00:02:16,250
Power Mochi!

9
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:31,230
You changed your clothes.

10
00:02:34,660 --> 00:02:36,110
It's quiet...

11
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:38,580
Almost too quiet...

12
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:44,660
All clear!

13
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:48,780
In any case, there's no way they'll
let us escape this easily.

14
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:51,590
The pride of an emperor is at stake.

15
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:53,450
Even so...

16
00:02:53,450 --> 00:02:57,590
our only option is to keep moving forward!

17
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,840
You're right!

18
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:02,390
In any case, we need to get back
on the straight course we were on earlier!

19
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,680
You're right.

20
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:10,380
If we can't meet up with Sanji-kun
and the others, who are bringing the cake,

21
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:13,080
not only will we remain separated,

22
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:18,040
we will face Big Mom's fury
like the scorn of hell itself.

23
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:32,460
To all the islands of Totto Land!

24
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:38,200
Dispatch all of the tarte ships
from each island immediately!

25
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:42,890
To save the Big Mom Pirates' prestige,

26
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:47,270
go after these three hateful pirate groups:

27
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:54,110
The Straw Hat crew, who wreaked havoc
upon us, the Big Mom Pirates;

28
00:03:54,110 --> 00:03:57,020
the group that stood beside them,

29
00:03:57,020 --> 00:04:02,090
the Fire Tank Pirates, who betrayed our queen, Big Mom,

30
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:04,370
and plotted to assassinate her;

31
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:09,560
and the missing fishmen,
allies of Knight of the Sea Jinbe,

32
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:12,310
who rebelled against us,

33
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:15,090
the Sun Pirates!

34
00:04:15,090 --> 00:04:21,720
Those pirates are currently in the midst
of escaping on the seas of Totto Land!

35
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:26,020
We're going to search for them?
What happened to the territorial sea slugs?

36
00:04:26,020 --> 00:04:29,070
Well, I heard they went missing.

37
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:31,100
What?!

38
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:35,820
Do not allow them to leave our territory!

39
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:39,230
Find them at all costs,

40
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:45,010
and sink every last one of them
as soon as you find them!

41
00:04:45,010 --> 00:04:49,510
Yeah!

42
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:53,240
What you just confirmed...

43
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:59,170
is that I am invincible
as long as I remain calm, right?

44
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:05,630
You'll drop your guard again!
You're an enemy...

45
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:08,220
that I can beat!

46
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:10,800
You're about to shrivel up, aren't you?

47
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:14,470
That's right! Gear Fourth's time limit is up!

48
00:05:14,470 --> 00:05:16,610
Okay, I'm done for now!

49
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:21,060
Thanks for warning me!

50
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:24,020
I won't be able to use haki for 10 minutes!

51
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:27,530
So I have to get as far away as I can!

52
00:05:27,530 --> 00:05:30,550
So, it's a power up with a time limit?

53
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:32,100
Flowing Mochi!

54
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:35,450
It'd be naive of me to just let you go!

55
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:47,590
Oh, no!

56
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:52,100
I just need 10 minutes!

57
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:54,600
Without haki,
there's no way I can beat him!

58
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,660
It's no good! I can't lose him!

59
00:05:58,660 --> 00:06:01,290
This is bad! Really bad!

60
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:06,750
How disappointing.
Is this really the end already?

61
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,350
Oh, no!

62
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:24,880
Huh? What just happened?!

63
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:27,830
Hey, what's wrong? Are you okay?!

64
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:30,950
All he did was taste the whipped cream...

65
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:34,080
D-Don't tell me it was poisoned...!

66
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:34,790
What?!

67
00:06:37,930 --> 00:06:39,970
Why don't you ask him?

68
00:06:39,970 --> 00:06:42,740
I could die right now...

69
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:46,850
I could die happily
because of how delicious this is!

70
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:49,340
He almost died
from tasting something delicious!

71
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:51,770
Look how happy he is!

72
00:06:51,770 --> 00:06:55,660
That whipped cream is
Sanji-san's secret ingredient!

73
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:58,500
The true power of sweetness!

74
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,230
It's finished!

75
00:07:03,230 --> 00:07:07,040
The ultimate cream, simsim whip!

76
00:07:03,230 --> 00:07:07,040
Simsim: Arabic for sesame

77
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:10,330
I-I wanna try it!

78
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:13,580
Pudding-chan, you can't taste it yet...

79
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,420
Huh?

80
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:19,050
We can't afford to lose
a dependable ally like you.

81
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,760
Don't fall before you even taste it!

82
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:34,650
If this cream were to be spread on a cake...

83
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:38,270
Don't think about it! You'll die!

84
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:49,080
My fluffy chiffon cake
is finished too, Black Leg!

85
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,370
Okay!

86
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:58,000
Hold it down!
It's so fluffy that it's gonna float away!

87
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,800
My part is finished, too!

88
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:03,280
In addition to Sanji-san's whipped cream,

89
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:07,850
we've got my super-sweet
and super-velvety chocolate!

90
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:14,730
Put a lid on it! It's smooth enough
to come flying out of the pot!

91
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:22,280
In five minutes, it'll be six p.m.

92
00:08:22,990 --> 00:08:25,560
Everything's going according to plan.

93
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:29,040
Is the ship ready?

94
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,540
Yes, sir!

95
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:35,040
To save time,
we'll finish the cake on the ship!

96
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:40,300
Let's rendezvous
with the Sunny as soon as possible!

97
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:42,010
Yes, sir!

98
00:08:42,010 --> 00:08:43,550
Okay!

99
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,760
It's finally time!

100
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,930
Now, let's go!

101
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:52,600
To take down the one causing trouble
for my friends: Big Mom!

102
00:08:58,330 --> 00:09:00,790
Sir Husband, why are you in disguise?

103
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:04,000
Because I'm shy.

104
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:14,680
Make way, everyone!
We're transporting the cake to the port!

105
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:18,060
Wow, amazing!
They made it that fast?!

106
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:19,940
The shape of the cake is complete!

107
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:22,230
And it smells really good!

108
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:27,060
Once it's complete,
I'm sure Mama will love it!

109
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:31,030
What a blissful aroma!
Are we in heaven?!

110
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:38,410
As expected of Madam Pudding,
Madam Chiffon,

111
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:40,910
and the WCI 31!

112
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:46,090
All right! Mama's coming!

113
00:09:46,090 --> 00:09:47,630
We need to move quickly!

114
00:09:48,210 --> 00:09:51,250
Madam Pudding! Madam Chiffon!

115
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:53,510
Take care!

116
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,370
Just you wait, Big Mom...

117
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:01,480
You will taste the ultimate cake!

118
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,590
Power Mochi!

119
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,560
Is that Brûlée?!

120
00:10:57,070 --> 00:11:00,440
Help! Big Brother!

121
00:11:02,740 --> 00:11:04,240
Help!

122
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,240
You fool!

123
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,820
Big Brother!

124
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:07,160
Why were you over there?!

125
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,620
Wait, Straw Hat!

126
00:11:12,050 --> 00:11:13,370
Dammit!

127
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,250
Brûlée!

128
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:26,460
That was close!

129
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:28,450
Where are we?

130
00:11:28,450 --> 00:11:30,870
Thank you, Branch!

131
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,310
The name's Brûlée!

132
00:11:33,310 --> 00:11:34,960
All right, let's wait here

133
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,330
until my Haki comes back!

134
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,290
W-What the...?!

135
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:10,220
Wedding...

136
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,670
Stop!

137
00:12:17,330 --> 00:12:20,280
This isn't it!

138
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:25,610
Mama, stop!
This is the island I govern!

139
00:12:25,610 --> 00:12:28,370
Mama! This is Nuts Island!

140
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:32,120
Neither the cake nor Straw Hat are here!

141
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:37,880
Where are you?! Straw Hat!

142
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:39,920
Big Mom?

143
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:56,930
Oh! That must be my daughter!

144
00:12:56,930 --> 00:13:00,880
Chiffon! It's no mistake!

145
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:05,410
Wait just a minute, Pudding!

146
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,710
That's...

147
00:13:09,710 --> 00:13:12,910
Brother Oven!
Please get out of our way!

148
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:16,650
Pudding, where are you taking that cake?!

149
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:19,570
I was told that you were
going to wait for the Straw Hats

150
00:13:19,570 --> 00:13:22,830
on this island, along with Mama
on her ravenous rampage.

151
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:28,170
We'll finish the cake on the ship
and stop Mama at sea!

152
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:29,790
At sea?!

153
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:33,960
Do you want us to let a rampaging Mama
land at Chocolat Town?!

154
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:38,050
If we contact Brother Peros,
we can arrange a meetup at sea!

155
00:13:47,770 --> 00:13:50,900
I see. You're right.

156
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:57,530
I understand.
My dear little sister, you may pass!

157
00:13:57,530 --> 00:14:01,990
Thank goodness!
Thank you, Big Brother Oven!

158
00:14:01,990 --> 00:14:03,530
But, Chiffon!

159
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:09,000
You're staying right here!

160
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,500
Sister Chiffon!

161
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:15,220
Oh, how cruel, Minister Oven!

162
00:14:15,220 --> 00:14:17,960
How could you do that to your little sister?!

163
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:25,850
It's none of your concern!
This is a family dispute!

164
00:14:25,850 --> 00:14:28,390
Let them take the cake to the port!

165
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:29,650
Yes, sir!

166
00:14:31,650 --> 00:14:33,270
Sister Chiffon!

167
00:14:34,570 --> 00:14:36,730
Chiffon-chan...

168
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:38,990
Chiffon...

169
00:14:38,990 --> 00:14:42,820
How dare you show your face in front of me!

170
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:47,030
You know what your husband plotted...

171
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:49,540
don't you?!

172
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:01,180
Even if you're family,
your betrayal is inexcusable!

173
00:15:04,350 --> 00:15:06,560
Stop it, Brother Oven!

174
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,430
Wait, Pudding-chan !

175
00:15:08,430 --> 00:15:11,600
If you do anything,
you'll be deemed a traitor, too!

176
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,810
What?

177
00:15:12,810 --> 00:15:16,900
Ah! He's worried about me!

178
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:23,700
But... I can't reveal myself
and fight, either...

179
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:30,260
What should I do?!

180
00:15:37,860 --> 00:15:42,110
I'm... already determined...!

181
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:47,990
My debt won't be fully repaid
until Nami and the others leave safely!

182
00:15:49,830 --> 00:15:55,250
I'll... help make the cake
until it's finished, Big Brother!

183
00:15:57,210 --> 00:16:03,090
They saved Lola's life...
I cannot fulfill my debt like this!

184
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:11,480
This is neither a simple fight between siblings nor a rebellious phase, Chiffon!

185
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:15,730
You are a traitor who plotted to kill the queen!

186
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:23,150
I never thought
I'd have to kill my own sister...

187
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:26,280
Stop, Big Brother!

188
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:29,780
We need to set an example
for the others in this country!

189
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:31,460
Sister Chiffon!

190
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:35,570
This is bad... Maybe I shouldn't be worried
about the consequences right now!

191
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:42,750
Get your hands
off of Chiffon, Oven-kun !

192
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:45,300
I'll save you right now,
my dear daughter!

193
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:46,550
Who's that?!

194
00:16:53,570 --> 00:16:58,080
You bastard!
I should've thrown you out to sea!

195
00:16:59,830 --> 00:17:01,870
I don't know who that guy is...

196
00:17:21,730 --> 00:17:23,890
but I better save her so quickly...

197
00:17:24,590 --> 00:17:26,440
that nobody sees me!

198
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:35,070
Hm? What?

199
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:37,530
We're gonna fly, Chiffon-chan.

200
00:17:37,530 --> 00:17:38,240
What?

201
00:17:47,630 --> 00:17:50,840
What? Did he just
knock down Minister Oven?!

202
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:53,960
Who is that old man?!

203
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:57,220
Am I stronger than I thought?

204
00:17:57,220 --> 00:17:59,100
Huh? Chiffon?

205
00:17:59,100 --> 00:18:01,050
There's no way that was you!

206
00:18:05,770 --> 00:18:08,290
Who was that just now?!

207
00:18:09,020 --> 00:18:10,270
Black Leg...

208
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:12,730
You're safe now, Chiffon-chan.

209
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:14,150
Thank you!

210
00:18:14,150 --> 00:18:16,700
Sister, you need to hide!

211
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:18,450
O-Okay.

212
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:21,910
Hurry to the port!

213
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:26,710
Make way!

214
00:18:29,670 --> 00:18:32,440
Black Leg saved me...

215
00:18:32,930 --> 00:18:34,510
but...

216
00:18:36,470 --> 00:18:39,960
who was that big guy?

217
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,050
There you are, Chiffon!

218
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,590
Stop it, Brother Oven!

219
00:19:03,590 --> 00:19:04,660
You little...

220
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:10,830
Wait! We need Sister Chiffon
in order to finish the cake!

221
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:13,600
Chiffon!

222
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:19,300
Stop! Get your hands off of Chiffon...

223
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:22,640
She's more than just an ungrateful child...

224
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:26,310
I'll burn you to the bone!

225
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,860
I guess I gotta go out there!

226
00:19:35,410 --> 00:19:37,010
What is it?!

227
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:39,790
Minister Oven, we found Bege's ship!

228
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:43,980
It's currently heading toward Cacao Island!

229
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:48,550
Our fleet is in pursuit!
We'll force them to land at the port!

230
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:51,340
Bege! You're kidding!

231
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:58,600
I thought he was a cold-hearted man, but he's come to rescue you, eh?!

232
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:00,720
Bege?!

233
00:20:03,950 --> 00:20:06,320
Bege!

234
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:09,160
It's me! Oven!

235
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:11,240
Oven?!

236
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:16,920
I just caught your accomplice, Chiffon,
on Cacao Island.

237
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,290
What?!

238
00:20:18,290 --> 00:20:18,740
Rero ?!

239
00:20:18,740 --> 00:20:20,590
The madam was captured?!

240
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:25,470
Right now, we are heading
toward the port from the town!

241
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:29,370
So you and your men
should come straight to the port

242
00:20:29,370 --> 00:20:31,010
and surrender yourselves!

243
00:20:31,970 --> 00:20:35,570
I am a man who's faithful to the law.

244
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:39,160
I won't be lenient
just because she's my little sister.

245
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:43,460
If you try anything funny,
then that'll be the end for her.

246
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:44,840
– What?!
– Rero ?!

247
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:47,920
Bege! Everyone!
Just turn around and run!

248
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:55,920
I came here out of my selfishness!
If you get caught, we'll all be executed anyway!

249
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:59,760
You guys should save yourselves, at least!

250
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:03,450
Mama hates me...

251
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:08,450
and you guys are...

252
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:11,040
my only real family!

253
00:21:26,870 --> 00:21:29,630
That's why, someday...

254
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:32,330
you should avenge me!

255
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:37,880
Madam, what are you saying?!

256
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:41,340
Madam!

257
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:49,100
Stop talking nonsense!

258
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:50,270
Chiffon!

259
00:21:52,650 --> 00:21:53,900
Oven!

260
00:21:53,900 --> 00:21:56,520
We'll arrive at the port soon!

261
00:21:56,520 --> 00:22:01,400
We'll disembark as you've requested...

262
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,990
Bege?!

263
00:22:02,990 --> 00:22:06,740
So don't lay another hand on Chiffon!

264
00:22:07,410 --> 00:22:08,830
Darling...

265
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:16,270
You're too soft, Bege.

266
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:19,690
That's going to cost you your head!

267
00:22:21,670 --> 00:22:24,360
Bege's ship is coming!

268
00:22:24,360 --> 00:22:27,700
All soldiers!
Get into a defensive formation!

269
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:34,330
Fleet! Split up to the right and to the left,
and block all escape routes!

270
00:22:34,330 --> 00:22:35,880
Yes, sir!

271
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:46,320
I can see Bege's ship!

272
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:50,360
I guess he really is going to surrender
without a fight, as he promised.

273
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:53,490
Minister Oven's carriage
is almost to the port!

274
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:56,430
Straw Hat?!

275
00:22:56,430 --> 00:22:57,030
What?!

276
00:22:57,030 --> 00:22:58,870
Straw Hat?! Brûlée?!

277
00:22:58,870 --> 00:23:01,400
Big Sister Amande!

278
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:04,270
What?! The pirate... Straw Hat Luffy?!

279
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:05,980
What's he doing here?!

280
00:23:05,980 --> 00:23:10,740
Mama, look!
Straw Hat is right there!

281
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,940
Straw Hat!

282
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:15,390
Why's Big Mom here?!

283
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:18,780
I thought she was chasing
the Sunny out at sea!

284
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:21,200
Help me, Mama!

285
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,510
Mama!

286
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:46,520
Oh, no! She's coming this way!

287
00:23:46,520 --> 00:23:52,400
Straw Hat! Where is my cake?!

288
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:54,690
I told you I don't know!

289
00:23:54,690 --> 00:23:58,070
Mama, Brother Peros! Help me!

290
00:23:58,070 --> 00:23:59,950
Let go of her!

291
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:02,620
Candy Wall!

292
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,750
Gear Third!

293
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:18,920
Gum-Gum...

294
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:21,430
Gigant Pistol!

295
00:24:26,850 --> 00:24:30,300
It's no good!
I can't break it without using haki!

296
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:32,900
Lick.

297
00:24:36,150 --> 00:24:37,860
It's surrounding us!

298
00:24:43,450 --> 00:24:44,870
Slow Waltz!

299
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:48,620
Yikes!

300
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:51,290
Big Sister! Don't cut me!

301
00:24:53,610 --> 00:24:59,550
My named blade, Shirauo, is craving blood...
I'll make you suffer before you die.

302
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:02,280
I can't fight you guys right now!

303
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:16,360
Mirror! Mirror!

304
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:19,070
Brother Peros!

305
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:21,700
Your candy is in my way!

306
00:25:22,390 --> 00:25:23,700
Candy Slug!

307
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:35,500
Give it to me!

308
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:38,210
The cake!

309
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:41,670
I have to keep running
until I regain my haki!

310
00:25:50,060 --> 00:25:52,580
Give it to me!

311
00:25:52,580 --> 00:25:55,050
The cake!

312
00:25:59,930 --> 00:26:03,600
Brother Peros, stop her!
This is my town!

313
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:07,310
Mama, you're way out of line!
You're wrecking the town!

314
00:26:09,060 --> 00:26:14,150
I won't let you get away, Straw Hat!

315
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:29,580
Damn! The town was completely destroyed!

316
00:26:37,710 --> 00:26:41,960
Hm? Where did Straw Hat go?!

317
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:46,300
Man, that was really close!

318
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:51,040
But if Big Mom is here,

319
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:55,220
that means Nami and the others
got away safely earlier, right?

320
00:27:03,570 --> 00:27:04,920
Ships!

321
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:08,280
The Big Mom Pirates
are catching up to us!

322
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:10,640
Roger! It's finally time!

323
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:13,550
Uh-huh! Running away is dull!

324
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:14,880
Let's fight them!

325
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:18,360
Yeah, leave it to us! Let's do it, Carrot!

326
00:27:20,520 --> 00:27:22,030
Carrot?

327
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:39,660
Carrot! I found you!

328
00:27:39,660 --> 00:27:42,910
A big battle is about to start!

329
00:27:44,220 --> 00:27:46,890
Hey, Chobro.

330
00:27:46,890 --> 00:27:47,980
Hm?

331
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:55,480
I wonder... if it'll be a full moon tonight...

332
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,110
Hm?!

333
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:20,830
Minister Oven!

334
00:28:45,730 --> 00:28:47,890
Those fools...

335
00:28:47,890 --> 00:28:51,100
We did it, Father!

336
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:56,520
Burn this into your eyes, Pez.

337
00:28:58,650 --> 00:29:02,980
This ish Papa's way of life.

338
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:06,450
Father!

339
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:14,740
Good job!

340
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:18,000
Now what are you gonna do?!
I'll follow your lead, Bege!

341
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:30,100
Somebody, help!

342
00:29:30,100 --> 00:29:31,340
Be quiet, Branch!

343
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:32,650
The name's Brûlée!

344
00:29:32,650 --> 00:29:36,340
This is Chips Town! Straw Hat Luffy is here!

345
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,680
Let go of me!

346
00:29:41,150 --> 00:29:42,860
This is Chockfull Town!

347
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:45,460
Straw Hat has been spotted!

348
00:29:45,460 --> 00:29:48,700
What?! Now he's in Chockfull Town?!

349
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:50,910
Straw Hat is emerging in different places!

350
00:29:50,910 --> 00:29:53,230
It looks like he's running around the Mirro-world!

351
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:57,550
Did Big Sister Brûlée get caught again?!

352
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,730
This is Green Town!

353
00:29:59,730 --> 00:30:07,140
We have received calls from multiple private residences
reporting that they saw someone suspicious!

354
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:18,540
What are you doing?! If you wanna escape,
why don't you go to Cacao Island already?!

355
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:20,930
What? How do you know about that?

356
00:30:20,930 --> 00:30:24,580
I eavesdropped!
Everyone knows now!

357
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:26,390
What?! Is that true?!

358
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:30,600
Just give up!
You can't beat my brother!

359
00:30:36,610 --> 00:30:38,870
Haki depletes as you use it...

360
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:49,670
If that guy's in a long, drawn-out fight, 
then his observation haki will definitely weaken!

361
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:56,130
You look like an idiot,
but you're a smart fighter.

362
00:30:56,130 --> 00:30:58,510
But that's not good enough!

363
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,730
Luffy.

364
00:31:03,730 --> 00:31:05,780
I've trained you,

365
00:31:05,780 --> 00:31:12,200
but haki is something that fully blooms
in the heat of a real battle.

366
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:18,240
By confronting strong enemies,
you will progressively get stronger!

367
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:26,380
I wonder if it's possible for me to see
slightly ahead into the future, too.

368
00:31:26,380 --> 00:31:30,670
What are you talking about?!
Don't get carried away, you pipsqueak!

369
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:45,060
I want to surpass him!

370
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:59,760
I want to beat him at full power!

371
00:32:01,410 --> 00:32:03,160
The man worth...

372
00:32:04,080 --> 00:32:06,330
one billion belly!

